CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 5, 1975, page 14, reads: "Mr. and Mrs. William Lewis.....admiring their gifts."
TitMainTitle: Women and men, including Mrs. William Lewis wearing fur stole, and Mr William Lewis wearing light colored suit with dark lapels and bow tie, posed behind banquet table in the Lemont Restaurant for 42nd wedding anniversary party in Mount Washington
